Emotional advertising ideas

The Garage Test

“If your trash can sat in your kitchen, how often would you clean it?”

The Summer Test

“The hotter it gets, the worse it gets.”

The Kid Test

Show a child grabbing the trash can lid before riding a bike.
“Little hands touch everything.”

The Nose Test

Someone opens the lid, recoils, then after your service opens it again without hesitation.
“Your nose knows.”

